When using RMPCDMD in a publication, please cite the following paper:

Pierre de Buyl, Mu-Jie Huang and Laurens Deprez. *RMPCDMD: Simulations of colloids with
coarse-grained hydrodynamics, chemical reactions and external fields*, arXiv:1608.04904
(2016).

available at https://arxiv.org/abs/1608.04904

Bibtex entry:

~~~
@Article{rmpcdmd_2016,
    eprint = {1608.04904},
    archivePrefix = {arXiv},
    journal = {arXiv},
    year = {2016},
    title = {{RMPCDMD: Simulations of colloids with coarse-grained hydrodynamics, chemical reactions and external fields}},
    author = {Pierre de Buyl and Mu-Jie Huang and Laurens Deprez}
}
~~~
